{"tid":907654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最近中共官媒係咁講\"楓橋經驗\"","createTime":"2018-11-19T03:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T02:45:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"76489ee004cfe60ce629b4678be1bb079cf3eb7d","tid":907654,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"中共官媒頌揚義和團及楓橋經驗 被疑宣傳排外思想 <br />\n<br />\n2018-11-18 22:25<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中共官媒人民報日前發表有關「楓橋經驗為何歷久彌新」文章，提到「楓橋經驗」實現了「捕人少、治安好」，能夠就地解決問題，不必往上呈報，新華社隨後發表了義和團相關文章。在中美關係緊張之餘，發表文章也被中國網友認為是宣傳「排外」思想。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>綜合外媒報導，楓橋經驗起源於1960年代的浙江省諸暨縣楓橋區，主張「就地化解矛盾，堅持矛盾不上交」。近期人民報記者採訪發源地浙江時，指出「它的內涵在新時代更加豐富」，從維護治安，進階到防範社會的任何安全風險。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>人民報的文章中說明，<span style=\"color: red;\">浙江省如今劃分成7.08萬個「網格」（安全責任區），每個網格皆配有1名專員，集各種職責於一身，全面取代各類村級協輔人員，透過「全科網格」，實現「小事不出村、大事不出鎮、微事不出格」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n新華社也發表「民族意識覺醒&mdash;&mdash;義和團反帝愛國運動」一文，寫到義和團先是反對帝國主義侵略，在壯大組織後，將矛頭指向外國強權，與八國聯軍抗爭，展現了百年前中國民眾團結禦侮的決心。<br />\n<br />\n文章在中國各大網路上不斷轉載，中國網民質疑，中美貿易戰風波未平，官媒發表的文章頗有「維穩」及「排外」含意，認為中國此舉如同在推廣這種維穩模式，日後中國言論自由將更加限縮。也有網友表示，義和團看似愛國，實際上卻是群「認不清世界大勢」的愚民，對宣揚愛國精神恐怕沒有太大用處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2616802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2616802&d=Q4iqH%2F1SCwOwE4sZZdxrgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=018314c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2616802&h=10b434a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2616802</a>"},{"pid":"1ad8444503b8bc4e385ed11d95023e55095c4bed","tid":907654,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:35:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>一場紀念楓橋經驗<span style=\"color: red;\">獲毛澤東批示55周年暨習近平批示15周年的會議12日在浙江紹興召開，</span></strong>中共政法委書記郭聲琨以及公安部、最高法院、最高檢察院的高官悉數出席。郭聲琨在會上表示，要以習近平的新時代中國特色社會主義思想為指引，堅定中國特色社會主義的社會治理之路，堅持創新發展新時代楓橋經驗，加快推進基層社會治理現代化，建設更高水平的平安中國。<br />\n<br />\n楓橋經驗是毛澤東於1960年代在浙江省寧波專區諸暨縣楓橋區（今為浙江省諸暨市楓橋鎮）創造的「發動群眾對階級敵人加強專政」的經驗，核心思想是矛盾在基層解決，不要延伸到中央層面，並要敢於發動民眾，提升民眾自治組織在基層治理中的作用。毛澤東於1963年在批示公安部的一個文件當中，特別提到楓橋經驗，並要求「各地仿效，經過試點，推廣去做」。<br />\n<br />\n自從改革開放以後，有關楓橋經驗的宣傳一度沉寂。直到2003年11月，時任浙江省委書記的習近平提出要推廣、創新楓橋經驗。2013年10月，時任中共總書記的習近平再度指示，要求堅持發展楓橋經驗，並將經驗與群眾路線進行聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有分析指稱，本次大會同時紀念毛澤東和習近平的批示，這在中共各種紀念大會非常罕見；</span></strong>習近平重提楓橋經驗釋放的政治信號，這是重新肯定改革開放前30年毛澤東的治國理念，也與習在2013年1月提出的「兩個不能否定」一脈相承。兩個不能否定是指「不能用改革開放後的歷史時期歷史否定改革開放前的歷史時期，也不能用改革開放前的歷史時期否定改革開放後的歷史時期」，這是習近平於2013年1月5日在中共中央黨校「新進中央委員、候補委員學習貫徹黨的十八大精神研討班」的講話中所提出...<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 郭聲琨：發展新時代楓橋經驗　加快推進基層社會治理 | ETtoday大陸 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181117/1308503.htm#ixzz5XGg9gCrO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181117%2F1308503.htm%23ixzz5XGg9gCrO&d=Q4iqH%2F1SCwOwE4sZZdxrgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f04efd33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181117/1308503.htm#ixzz5XGg9gCrO</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"e50b82816b1af40879c646e64893320367407728","tid":907654,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"即係就地解決，唔好俾上面知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea71ffa16c521f085913a6ee85a4e6ccc4c4d1b6","tid":907654,"uid":11798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"大事化小 小事化無<br />\n讓民眾啞起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dbfb5d313ce3af3df9b02bfddf5d363d2dbb85","tid":907654,"uid":18912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"唔俾人上訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7839e0974457f915a4984275360a3434aaf3852a","tid":907654,"uid":192068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e50b82816b1af40879c646e64893320367407728","tid":907654,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"即係就地解決，唔好俾上面知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:40:22.000Z","msg":"即係鼓勵私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dafc9aa7c7de2c0529e758a235f4c0a1d7c971","tid":907654,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50b82816b1af40879c646e64893320367407728","tid":907654,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"即係就地解決，唔好俾上面知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f13682d92e4e80340b66ff102f3887fbf529f5","tid":907654,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e50b82816b1af40879c646e64893320367407728","tid":907654,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"即係就地解決，唔好俾上面知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:50:04.000Z","msg":"1)群眾<del>鬥</del>監察群眾, 9X%人對最反叛幾%人&quot;進行教育、評審和說理鬥爭&quot;<br />\n2) 黨地位問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下面兩篇值得一讀<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;四類分子&rdquo;指地主、富農、反革命和其他壞分子。不難看出，&ldquo;楓橋經驗&rdquo;是中共改造&ldquo;四類分子&rdquo;的經驗。1978年底，中共決定給四類分子摘帽，使2,000 万人結束長期受歧視的生活。1979年2月，中共喉舌《人民日報》文章《摘掉一頂帽，調動几代人》披露，当時楓橋有人口13.7万人，历年戴帽的四類分子有3,279人，大約每50個人中就有一個&ldquo;四類分子&rdquo;。当時左禍之嚴重可見一斑。 ...轉自多維新聞網<a href=\"http://www.dwnews.com/big5/...1542598868150...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dwnews.com%2Fbig5%2F...1542598868150...&d=Q4iqH%2F1SCwOwE4sZZdxrgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8ca32f41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dwnews.com/big5/...1542598868150...</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">發展是硬道理，穩定也是硬道理，抓發展、抓穩定兩手都要硬。</span></span></strong> 堅定不移走中國特色社會主義社會治理之路，把黨的群眾路線堅持好、貫徹好，讓&ldquo;楓橋經驗&rdquo;在新時代發揚光大，提高社會治理社會化、法治化、智能化、專業化水平，加快形成共建共治共享的社會治理格局，我們就一定能確保人民安居樂業、社會安定有序、國家長治久安。<br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fopinion.people.com.cn%2Fn1%2F2018%2F1113%2Fc1003-30396430.html&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com.hk%2Ftranslate%3Fsl%3Dzh-CN%26tl%3Dzh-TW%26js%3Dy%26prev%3D_t%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ie%3DUTF-8%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fopinion.people.com.cn%252Fn1%252F2018%252F1113%252Fc1003-30396430.html%26edit-text%3D%26act%3Durl&d=Q4iqH%2F1SCwOwE4sZZdxrgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=07fd5ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fopinion.people.com.cn%2Fn1%2F2018%2F1113%2Fc1003-30396430.html&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url</a>"},{"pid":"96b363780474c68874452fdfda6d0fbb1e248287","tid":907654,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都係咁咩"},{"pid":"c02914f13482b65ce735b23058174697b79f13ab","tid":907654,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"解決提出問題的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a437a861b6af83f96da9fa7e12af9b9fea8e89f","tid":907654,"uid":66784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"意思姐係基於成本問題，政府力量將會撤岀農村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a30aaa415ac93b338f3112b0a2b6